author: @robinshot1806
text:
傻B精液猪、傻B疯狗、傻B老黑黑黑黑黑佛鱼、傻B老赵、傻B老郭，就知道欺负无辜的人，赶快把我的人和我的粉丝放了！卸掉她们保护层又吸毒又放鬼，还敢在外围抓起来要杀要砍往死了吓唬？！敢动她们一手指头我把你们全塞绞肉机里，人渣肉沫扔到海里，拿你们屁股蛋钓鲨鱼！！！

傻B一群，现在又改规则，赌我不敢放心让我的人缠保护层，再催眠我一点点儿，好像不清醒的感觉一样，让我感觉不到是催眠，以为是灵感真相，你们知道我一定可以发现并且放大来思考，因为我的灵魂敏感！所以你们赌我一定反抗，以为保护层是害我的毒品，精神激动继续战斗，继续弄伤自己，你们就有机会拐骗我的粉丝，和把我的人引出来占便宜！做梦去吧你们！一群心理变态的吸毒鬼！我什么脑子？！早把你们看明明白白的了！再秘密研究怎么攻击我的rose和我的人，把你们全杀光骨灰倒马桶里！

还来？！还催眠我安全是假象，激我奋起反抗？！你他妈的吃饱了撑的是不？！磨叽个鸡巴毛，赶紧滚！！！

author: @zhongqixu5854
text:
傻B精液猪，傻B疯狗，居然把大混混们的混蛋同学找来，亏本换游戏币趁我虚偷袭我？！又是催眠又是抹油又是偷运气又是锁定我记忆又是让我放松，还手机上拉屎忽悠我？！知道打不过我，时间也拖不久了，想在阳光照到我之前趁乱抓我脸一把就跑？！偷鸡摸狗的下三滥，以为我看不出来吗？就知道你们发现阳光快来了孤注一掷，临死也要咬我一口，假装准备下一步攻击削弱我让我睡不着觉做不了梦，然后在下一场游戏开始前提前下狠手，短时间拼命下黑手抓我的粉丝！一群赖皮、发疯畜生！居然还赌我看不出来不是在比赛抢人，而是在打架保护人，还猜不透不许我们的人出来？！居然还催眠我把我往以前比赛抢人的记忆里拖，还催眠我点放不出人帮忙的视频？！一天就知道吸毒作弊，一群垃圾！！！赔死你们！！！我彻底不受以前记忆影响了，留言也发了，现在心服口服了吧？！哭吧，疯狗们！

滚滚滚滚滚滚滚滚滚滚滚滚！！！！！！！！！！傻B老黑……佛鱼，傻B老赵，傻B老郭，永远在马桶里锁着吧，一堆臭狗屎！！！！！！！！回回躲在黑暗中偷窥，等我出完招了你们出来偷袭我，你们等着啊，早晚为国家彻底灭了你们这群贪吃害虫！谁敢动我的人我杀了你们家，跟我做对就等着遭天谴，不得好死、下地狱吧！！！！

author: @Djfjfjrhhrjrhrhfj
text: 1:50 Nayeon does this dance better than the rest of the group. It's because of the way she leans in and out so prominently, uses great hand placement, does mesmerizing body rolls, and has a fierceness to her facial expressions while dancing. She hits the moves slowly, smoothly, and with great rhythm. The other girls do it fine too, but the most satisfying is watching Nayeon do it, almost feels like shes moving in slow motion.

text:
For new onces and people that are confused on who's who :)
Nayeon: black pants, medium length brown hair with bangs, white sleeves (0:12)
Jeongyeon: she isn't here because she's on hiatus. We love you Jeongyeon!! <3
Momo: short-ish light brown hair with bangs, black pants, black top, black sleeves (0:16)
Sana: medium length blonde hair, black long sleeved crop top, white pants (0:20)
Jihyo: dark brown hair in a bun, white crop top, white pants, black sleeves (1:07)
Mina: short dark brown hair, black crop top, gray sweatpants, gray sleeves (1:41)
Dahyun: long black hair, black crop top, white pants, black sleeves (1:35)
Chaeyoung: long blonde hair with bangs, black sports bra, brown/olive pants and jacket (1:31)
Tzuyu: medium length brown and faded purple hair, black crop top, black pants, white sleeves (0:25)

Hope this helped!! And if you don't know who do you think the visual or visuals are??

author: @vwd6116
text:
Aw, man... Jeongyeon's got to do more of these OT9 dance practice videos when she gets back. I really cannot get used to these empty spaces where she should be dancing with the rest of TWICE. I hope she's well on the road to recovery this time. This has got to be one of the longest OT8 spells for TWICE. JYPE ought to give them some more R&R and continue to polish their English at the least. 

I really don't like how these Western shows tend to portray K-pop groups as trends when they're way more than that these days. 

I like the formation and choreography on this one. It's reminiscent of "Feel Special" but a bit slicker -smoother to track. At least they're not as out of breath by the end just like how "More & More" was.

text:
Initially, i have doubts about this song because you know, this is their first full English single so having worries it might not live up to expectations is inevitable.

But after listening to it multiple times, i realized my doubts are uncalled for. This song is amazing! Beautiful lyrics, choreography that doesn't look tedious and of course, the overflowing visuals of the members, just round up the song perfectly.

In conclusion, its a bop and you can't skip the song (unless you are being an a**hole then i have no words.)

P.S.: Sana making my heartrate goes abnormally fast whenever the camera pans too close to her.
